ActBritish Columbia Treaty Commission Act
PrecisRe-appointment of JERRY LAMPERT of Vancouver, British Columbia, as Commissioner of the British Columbia Treaty Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months or until such time as a new Commissioner is appointed, whichever occurs first.
